### **邮件模板（英文版）**

**Subject:** Request for Recommendation Letter for National Interest Waiver Application

Dear [Professor/Dr. Last Name],

I hope this message finds you well. I am writing to kindly ask if you would be willing to provide a letter of recommendation for me to support my application for the **National Interest Waiver (NIW)**. As part of the application, I am required to submit recommendations from experts in my field who can attest to my academic contributions and their impact on advancing scientific knowledge and healthcare technologies.

I greatly value your expertise and the significance of your work in the field, and I believe your endorsement of my research would be a powerful testament to its relevance and importance. My work, particularly in the area of **epileptic seizure prediction using machine learning** and **EEG signal classification**, has had considerable influence in advancing predictive healthcare technologies, as highlighted by numerous citations, including those from your recent research.

If you agree to support my application, I would be happy to provide any additional information or materials, including a draft of the recommendation letter if needed, to make the process as smooth as possible. The deadline for submission is [insert deadline], and I would be incredibly grateful if you could accommodate this timeline.

Thank you very much for considering my request. I truly appreciate your time and support, and I look forward to hearing from you soon.

Warm regards,  
**Wenbin Hu**  
[Your Contact Information]  
[Your Position]  
[Your Institution]

